channel.title: Can not find symbol Error
channel.description:
[B]I'm trying to show my lottery fund in the quest tab but it says it can't find the symbol c.fund. Any idea how I can solve this?[/B]
[CODE]src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:318: error: cannot find symbol c.getPA().sendFrame126("Current Draw: @gre@"+ c.fund +"", 7334); ^ symbol: variable fund location: variable c of type Client Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/CODE]
[b]I did import the lottery class in playerAssistant.java[/b]
[CODE]import server.model.minigames.lottery;[/CODE]
